This folder contains npm images of Wijmo library core and Angular 2 interop modules, 
in different module formats.

wijmo-<module_format>-min subfolders contain minified JavaScript modules 
in <module_format>, their typings and metadata for Angular 2 AoT compiler.

If you are an owner of a licensed version of Wijmo, the folder also includes 
wijmo-<module_format>-src subfolders, which contain TypeScript sources, 
non-minified JavaScript modules and mapping files.

Please refer to readme.txt file included in each subfolder for more details.
